data.description:
Beautiful Lakefront Home Featuring Washer & Dryer Included, Formal Living Room and Family Room w/ Wood Burning Fireplace, Split Bedrooms, 2'' Wood Blinds Throughout, Large Screened and Tiled Patio Overlooking Lake and Large Producing Orange Tree in Yard.                                 
                                                                                     
Directions; Take San Jose to Sunbeam Rd, Left on Craven to a Left on Old Spanish and a Left on Arch Creek to a Right on Caraway.
